snippet.title: Eminem's Reaction To Machine Gun Kelly's "Rap Devil": "It's Not Bad... For Him"
snippet.description:
Eminem is back with Part II of The Kamikaze Interview with Sway Calloway. Once again, the two Hip Hop aficionados dive into a bevy of topics, including the real reason Em dissed Machine Gun Kelly on “Not Alike” and his relationship with Joe Budden.

For the full story on Eminem, Joe Budden and MGK check out HipHopDX.com:
https://hiphopdx.com/news/id.48428/title.eminem-reveals-reason-for-joe-budden-diss-why-he-came-for-machine-gun-kelly
